      "comment": "LIVIN' LAVISH (6) resumed in a Grade 4/5 at this track and finished sixth over 400m (23.06). Solid record at the distance winning three races. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SASSY GAL (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (30.37) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Sale. Solid record at the distance winning four races. One of the better hopes. FLAMING FOX (1) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 2 lengths from the winner Evil Eye in third(19.65) at Healesville. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and three minor placings from seven starts. Expecting another good run. MISS INDI BEAR (4) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into second last time out (22.81) over 400m at this track.",
